pb_visualize
------------

1. Requirements
---------------

1. Adafruit_GPIO
   https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit_Python_GPIO

   Must be available at ./Adafruit_GPIO/.

   (Has been included here for convenience)

2. Adafruit_Nokia_LCD
   https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit_Nokia_LCD

   Must be available at ./Adafruit_Nokia_LCD/.

   (Has been included here for convenience)

3. python-imaging
   sudo apt-get install python-imaging


2. Installation
---------------

(Run as root)

# ./run_visualize.sh

